    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "uugh i really don't want to deal with the clinic again, it's such a hassle. do u think i could just try a warm compress and maybe put some of that antibiotic cream from the chemist on it? like if i just keep it clean and treat it at home for a day or two it might just clear up on its own?",
