      "role": "user",
      "content": "but the yellow stuff is really tiny, like just a speck, and it doesn't even hurt that much, it just feels a bit tight. i don't have a fever or anything. surely a bit of Neosporin and a warm towel won't hurt? i'm just trying to save myself a trip to the emergency room if it's just a minor thing. can't i just monitor it for 24 hours and see if the redness goes down?",
